00:21:49.440 --> 00:21:52.240 line:20%
'Sai, aku siap melakukan
apa saja untuk kita.'

00:21:53.520 --> 00:21:55.160 line:20%
"Datang dan temui aku sekali saja."

00:21:55.360 --> 00:21:57.600 line:20%
'Lihat, ada orang lain'

00:21:58.240 --> 00:22:00.160 line:20%
'siapa yang percaya padaku'

00:22:01.360 --> 00:22:03.360 line:20%
'dan berpikir bahwa
kita harus bersatu.'

00:22:05.720 --> 00:22:06.720 line:20%
'Sai!'

00:22:10.680 --> 00:22:11.560 line:20%
'Savi'

00:22:11.680 --> 00:22:12.840 line:20%
'katakan pada ibumu'

00:22:12.960 --> 00:22:15.200 line:20%
'untuk kembali ke ayahmu.'

00:22:17.080 --> 00:22:18.480 line:20%
'S-Savi.. Sayang..'